gantt
  title Release cutover plan
  dateFormat  YYYY-MM-DD
  axisFormat  %b %d

  section Prep
  Freeze release branch     :done, prep1, 2026-04-20, 1d
  Draft notes              :active, prep2, 2026-04-21, 2d

  section Validation
  Smoke test               :test1, after prep2, 1d
  Sign-off                 :test2, after test1, 1d

  section Ship
  Publish release          :ship1, after test2, 1d
